				<textElement textAlignment="Justified"/>
				<text><![CDATA[Thank you for your business. All shipments FOB North Adams, Massachusetts or Erie, CO. Payment terms calculated from invoice date. Late payments subject to interest charges and late payment fees. No returns without authorization. Authorized returns subject to a restock and rework fee. See Dealer Terms & Conditions for full details.
]]></text>
